(a) a description of the main characteristics of the payment service to be provided; 
(b) a specification of the information or unique identifier that has to be provided by the payment service user in order 
for a payment order to be properly initiated or executed; 
(c) the form of and procedure for giving consent to initiate a payment order or execute a payment transaction and 
withdrawal of such consent in accordance with Articles 64 and 80;
